NUMBER 1211
NAME Quicksilver Pond
FOREST
OBSCURED_DAY_LIGHT
REGION 15
CHANNEL 68
MONSTER_GROUP 36
CALL 69
CALL 33
*DESCRIPTION_START
Tall indigo reeds ring a small, perfectly circular pond like impossibly
slender sentinels watching over a sacred place. The water's surface is
smooth and mirror-bright, unbroken by even the slightest ripple, and
reflects back its surroundings in an exact yet reversed image. It is a
curious impression, that the reflection may be as real as what casts it.
*DESCRIPTION_END
