ITEM 0 704 ADJ1=265 ADJ2=658 ADJ3=36 
; round silvery bright pond (leading up to Dark Stream)
ITEM 1 76 ADJ1=210 ADJ2=350 VAL2=1212 
; narrow winding trail (leading up to Weeping Willow)
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 0
The images seen in the pool's reflection are remarkably clear and sharp.
The longer one looks at them, the harder it becomes to tell where the known
reality leaves off and the pictures begin. Although eerie, there seems no
malevolence behind this strange alteration to perception; nevertheless, it
is wise to remember that the unknown may still be dangerous even though it
might not intend to be.
*DESCRIPTION_END
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 1
