NUMBER 1214
NAME Mysterious Shrine
FOREST
OBSCURED_DAY_LIGHT
REGION 15
CHANNEL 68
MONSTER_GROUP 36
CALL 69
CALL 33
*DESCRIPTION_START
The mist thins mysteriously after several paces, revealing what must be the
far end of the clearing. Countless huge, ancient trees hem in the area on
three sides. A roiling wall of fog marks the way back, but exactly which
direction that really is seems impossible to tell. A massive altar made from
an unknown black stone rises above the tall grasses, flanked by two large
statues also fashioned from the same dark substance. The shadows loom long
and dark here, regardless of the time of day, as though the place hovers
eternally in a sort of twilight unrelated to the passage of the sun overhead.
