*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAMINE 0
Nothing but opaque, clinging dampness meets the eye, beading one's eyelashes
with tiny droplets of water.
*DESCRIPTION_END
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAMINE 1
Although stone, the angles of the altar are strangely fluid and organic, as
though it had been grown rather than carved. Stylized, petrified brambles
coil up the four corners from the base. Tiny alien runes can be glimpsed
amongst the leaves and thorns, traced by flickers of eldtritch fire so deep
a green in color it is nearly black.
*DESCRIPTION_END
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAMINE 2
He stands proud and magnificent, mane rippling and nostrils flared. His horn
is polished to an iridescent, glossy sheen.
*DESCRIPTION_END
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAMINE 3
Her face is serene and perhaps a little sad, yet her eyes burn with fierce
strength that is more than mildly disconcerting.
*DESCRIPTION_END
