IFPREVERB BREAK 2
   CLEARVERB
   ECHO PLAYER The corpse stirs, turning toward you, evil light flaring in its eyesockets.
   ECHO OTHERS %N attempts to destroy the corpse, but it stirs, reaching out for %N.
   DAMAGEPLR BODYONLY 100 You feel some of your life energy drained from you!
   PLREVENT 1
   CONTPLREVENT
   ECHO PLAYER Your legs buckle and you sink to your knees, shuddering.
   ECHO OTHERS %N sinks slowly to %h knees, shuddering uncontrollably.
   POSITION KNEEL
ENDIF
IFVERB RECALL 2
   IFVAR SKILL32 > 3
      ECHO PLAYER Though only tatters of skin remain, judging from what remains of his face,
      ECHO PLAYER you guess that he might once have been one of the darkweaver race that seems
      ECHO PLAYER to be native to Blackthorn Forest.
   ENDIF
ENDIF
IFPREVERB2 PUT 2
   ECHO ALL %N puts something into the hollow ribcage of the corpse.
   REMOVEITEM -1
   PLREVENT 1
   CONTPLREVENT
   ECHO ALL A dull greenish-yellow glow engulfs the item, briefly hiding it from view.
   PLREVENT 1
   CONTPLREVENT
   ECHO ALL When the light fades again, the item has vanished, completely absorbed.
   GMMSG %N is feeding the lich in the burial mound. This is a slightly evil thing to do.
ENDIF
;
NUMBER 1234
NAME Atop a Hill
PLAIN
OBSCURED_DAY_LIGHT
REGION 15
CHANNEL 68
CALL 33
*DESCRIPTION_START
Up here, the ground dry and dusty, barren except for a sparse cover of the
hardiest plant life. The dirt gives slightly when weight is put upon it, a
discomfiting reminder that the mound underfoot is hollow and not necessarily
very sturdy. In fact, the center of the dome has sunken in slightly to form
a slight depression full of pebbles and clumps of dirt.
*DESCRIPTION_END
EXIT D 1203
IFVERB JUMP -1
   DISBAND
   ECHO PLAYER The ground beneath you suddenly gives way!
   ECHO OTHERS The ground beneath %N suddenly gives way!
   MOVE 1233
   ; into Burial Chamber
   EQUAL ROUNDTIME 5
   AFFECT 1233
   ECHO ALL %N tumbles through a hole in the ceiling, landing with a muffled thud.
   DAMAGEPLR CRUSH 30 You fall fifty feet onto a hard stone and dirt floor.
   POSITION LAY
   RANDOM MONSTERALERT 1 50 0
   IFVAR MONSTERALERT < 5
      PLREVENT 2
      CONTPLREVENT
      ECHO ALL A chilling voice rasps, "You shall pay for desecrating my tomb and disturbing my rest."
      GENMON 16
      ; lich
      GENMON 98
      GENMON 98
      ; shadow guardian
      AFFECT 1234
   ENDIF
   AFFECT 1234
ENDIF
IFVERB DIG -1
   DISBAND
   ECHO PLAYER The ground beneath you suddenly gives way!
   ECHO OTHERS The ground beneath %N suddenly gives way!
   MOVE 1233
   ; into Burial Chamber
   EQUAL ROUNDTIME 5
   AFFECT 1233
   ECHO ALL %N tumbles through a hole in the ceiling, landing with a muffled thud.
   DAMAGEPLR CRUSH 30 You fall fifty feet onto a hard stone and dirt floor.
   POSITION LAY
   RANDOM MONSTERALERT 1 50 0
   IFVAR MONSTERALERT < 5
      PLREVENT 2
      CONTPLREVENT
      ECHO ALL A chilling voice rasps, "You shall pay for desecrating my tomb and disturbing my rest."
      GENMON 16
      ; lich
      GENMON 98
      GENMON 98
      ; shadow guardian
      AFFECT 1234
   ENDIF
   AFFECT 1234
ENDIF
;
